long_description:
Screw holes for standard 350w power supply. Designed for Meanwell LRS-350, but most other 350w standard size power supplies have same hole layouts.
Hole size is 4mm - designed for screws to pass through material and into power supply from below.

Screw holes for Raspberry PI Model 3 which is the latest Raspberry PI model. NOTE: All the raspberry PI models have different mounting hole placements.
Hole size is 2.34mm - designed for 4-40 screw / standoff

6 mounting holes for the SanDevice 16 channel pixel controller. This is for Revision 1.3 of the Board
Hole size is 2.34mm - designed for 4-40 screw / standoff

Screw holes for ESPixel Pops which is a through hole pixel controller which runs the ESPixelStick software.
Hole size is 2.34mm - designed for 4-40 screw / standoff
This component will create a circle hole which is sized to fit a 3/4 knockout clamp
This component will create a circle hole and screw holes sized to fit a 40mm fan
Screw holes for Pop Power Fanout / Power Distribution board.  Revision 1.2 of board.
Creates to square holes which a zip tie can be run between to hold wires down
Screw holes for CFOL Power Distro 4 board.  Revision 1.1 of board.
Screw holes for official ESPixelStick which runs the ESPixelStick software.
4 Port Fuse Holder creates screws designed for a 4mm screw.
Screw Holes for Sandevice 4 port pixel controller

short_description: Andy Harrison Power Distro Rev B
